data.description: Beautifully updated home with tons of great features located near Bass Park. The floorplan has two living rooms, one of which seamlessly flows into the kitchen, and an office that has a view of the pool.  Kitchen has large island which has a countertop overhang making a great breakfast bar.  Updates completed May 2022 include all paint, flooring, granite counter tops throughout, stainless appliances, back splash, all plumbing fixtures and light fixtures, bathtub and shower tile surrounds, sinks, cabinet and door hardware, pool plaster and tile, pool equipment, and much more. The backyard is a great summertime spot with a covered patio and diving pool.
